explanation: "THRIVE = High-flow nasal oxygen during apnea<br><br>Benefits:<br><br>* extends safe apnea time\n* provides low-level PEEP\n* humidified + warmed gas\n* useful in obese + OSA + difficult airway<br><br>CO\u2082: not fully eliminated, accumulates but slower\nTransnasal Humidified Rapid Insufflation Ventilatory Exchange",
