explanation: "A non-rebreathing mask is identified by its **reservoir bag** and **one-way valves**, allowing delivery of high FiO\u2082 (up to 90\u2013100%). These features distinguish it from Hudson, Venturi, or nebulizer masks.<br><br><img src=\"https://corebtr-assets-production.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/question_explanation/90bba81b-f86c-4c67-9ef2-5ca1da784a46.jpg\" alt=\"Uploaded Image\"><br><br><br>",
