text: "This position is given in which patients?",
options: [{"id": "A", "text": "Pulse absent Breathing present", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "B", "text": "Pulse absent Breathing absent", "is_correct": false}, {"id": "C", "text": "Unconscious with Pulse present Breathing present", "is_correct": true}, {"id": "D", "text": "Conscious with Pulse present Breathing present", "is_correct": false}],
explanation: "The position shown is the **recovery position**, used for an **unconscious patient who has a pulse and is breathing**. It maintains airway patency, prevents tongue obstruction, and reduces the risk of aspiration by allowing secretions to drain.",
